Atlantis City.Description: An underwater city enclosed in a glass dome.

Baguette.Description: The northern territory of MasterInventor's Yugoslavian state.

Banapo.Description: Located in the swamps and dark forests, Banapo is one of the older nations on the server.

Bialya.Description: Bialya is a small country in the southeast corner of the map. Its mission is to have the largest farms and undercut every other nations' prices, and is always looking for new members and allies.

Botania.Description: This archipelago of 7 islands was gifted to Goomlandia by Vanskovich and heavily developed as a "vacation paradise" before being bombed extensively in the Vansk-Fiannan War and subsequently being abandoned. However, Novosibirsk remains as an underground city on the southeasternmost island.

Bowilla's Basedments.Description: A series of uniquely themed basements under the north side of Goomtown.

Cascadia.Description: Cascadia is a peaceful Yugoslavian state in the birch forests of the West. Its calm landscape features several cultural monuments along with the famed dark prismarine mob grinder.

Castle Montrose.Description: The original building in Montrose, Castle Montrose holds the main storage for Montrosian citizens, as well as a variety of workbenches and functional blocks.

Cattlehead.Description: A historic suburb northwest of Goomtown, originally constructed on land gifted to Goomlandia by Voidnest after the split of Goomnest. It marks the original spot of the Goomtown Wall, laid to protect against the adjacent VOC, then an independent splinter state.

Champignon.Description: A suburb east of Goomtown, it is the longtime home of Grooge64 and the second-oldest settlement in Goomlandia, being constructed as a home for villagers just after Bageltown was founded in December 2018. It features several Gabe heads and stands at the crossroads of the Goomlandian Mesa and Goomtown.

Championis.Description: A state formed by Pawnch_ when his wilderness base was exposed by MiksaSerbia.

Cratertown.Description: Once a planned Goomnest settlement, the project was later abandoned and lay empty until Goomtown expanded into it a year later. Cratertown now boasts attractions such as the golden Cheesegrate Tower, George the giant chicken, and the Nether-themed Goomtown PVP arena.

East Goomtown.Description: A neighborhood of Goomtown, it is really the south-central of the city, despite the name. It is mostly residential but has several businesses and storages.

East Taiga.Description: A colony in the South owned by HUM, containing the Tautona bunker.

Falcon's Nest.Description: The famed PVP arena located in the southern part of Fianna.

Federal Province.Description: The capital of the Sylvian Union.

Fianna.Description: Fianna is a kingdom located on Dwarf Island.

Gabeford.Description: Gabeford is one of the oldest personal estates on the server, owned by Header of Montrose FlyingGMM. It contains several farms and secondary buildings, a dock, and FlyingGMM's signature square cobblestone house.

Glavnaya.Description: The historical and cultural capital of Vanskovich, it has seen many battles and changed hands many times throughout history. Also partially destroyed in the Vansk-Fiannan War, it has since been rebuilt and is a thriving Goomlandian city-island.

GoatWear Island.Description: The only mushroom island in the world.

Goomtown.Description: The cultural and economic center, and the capital of Goomlandia, it is one of the largest and oldest cities in the world. Originally named Bageltown, it has a long and colorful history and a large amount of tourist attractions.

Groogelandia.Description: A large Goomlandian forest colony and the site of Propaganda Island. The city of Vilnius lies to the south, settled by crazyjuplup.

HomeofBrave.Description: AdilOzbay's objectively superior state in the North.

HUM.Description: Properopolis is the capital of HUM, the oldest nation in the world. HUM has historically operated a confidential banking service based in Properopolis, providing non-partisan safe storage and interest-gaining accounts which has made the state quite wealthy.

Hybrasil.Description: Hybrasil is a state of Yugoslavia, inhabited by Katawicz and focused on large-scale resource production.

Icedale Tavern.Description: A historic location and IBWH site of the Icedale Guild.

Ilyrdom.Description: The historic city of Ilyrdom, now occupied by the Schevakian Empire.

Inquisition.Description: The southern territories of MasterInventor's Yugoslavian state.

Iris.Description: Iris is the Montrosian estate of argetlam04, including the famous "arget Museum", a collection of historic objects.

Isle of Gold.Description: The easternmost part of the Goomlandian province of Gold Coast, Isle of Gold is shaded by the World Tree located on the Grove Tribe-owned plateau above the island.

Lazarica.Description: Lazarica is a historic state in Yugoslavia, containing the classic mob grinder and the Yugoslavian mesa.

MBL & MVPC.Description: The MBL (Montrosian Bureau of Logistics) holds the Montrosian Quartiermeister's office and serves as a place for general storage. The MVPC is Montrose's villager breeder & trading hall.

MID.Description: The Montrose Industrial District (MID for short) is Montrose's industrial hub, featuring a mob grinder, pumpkin farm, villager breeder, and iron farm.

Montrose Ice Farm.Description: The ice farm employed by the Montrose Nether Company.

Montrosian Government Offices.Description: The currently vacant offices of the Montrosian government.

Montrosian Prismarine Farm.Description: Montrose's prismarine farm in the south seas.

Montrosian Production Emporium.Description: A production facility which aims to produce every resource that can be produced passively. It serves as a 'living seed bank', providing public access to each type of crop and livestock for individuals to found their own farms.

New Toeland.Description: Once part of the small nation of Banastair before it migrated to become modern-day Banapo, New Toeland has changed hands many times throughout history, but remains still uninhabited. The province's only permanent settlement is Stemtown in the northwest.

Northbay.Description: The former Wohlstandian village of Northbay.

Novosibirsk.Description: A project by DoctorProck, it is an underground city built into a ravine in the southeastern Botanian Isles and is the only permanent settlement there. It connects via underwater tunnel to Rapture and Vailan-owned Atlantis.

Ozai.Description: Ozai is a nation of merchants and traders on the southwestern side of the map, near the icefields and southern taiga.

Prosperity League HQ.Description: The headquarters of the former Prosperity League, a multinational alliance including Montrose, HUM, Rhett, Bagelonia, The Guardian State, and Lucas.

Rapture.Description: The famous underwater residence of MTJNC. Rapture also features a massive mob grinder and modern architecture spanning several islands in the West Sea.

Rhett Island.Description: Rhett Island is the mainland of Rhett, located in the westernmost portion of Tierra Del Fuego. Covered in podzol, this is the site of many iconic Rhettian builds ("cool stuff").

Richard.Description: The most developed of the Goomlandian mesa provinces, it hosts several fortifications, an airstrip, redstone projects, ancient habitations, and a giant woolen Goomy billboard. It was once an independent nation under Carpo_Diem, which later merged into Mesadonia and moved southward to Mesadonia2.

Sable-Rouge.Description: An ancient ghost town in southeastern Clappia that was built to assert Goomlandian presence in that province that had been recently purchased from ClapYoThighs, it was once as busy and bustling as Goomtown (then called Bageltown) but faded in importance as Bageltown became the center of commerce and culture.

Schenektengrad.Description: One of the most populated cities on the landscape, Schenektengrad is also one of the most war-torn, suffering significant fire damage during the Balkan Troubles.

Soleil Islands.Description: These islands have been Soraryian, Yugoslavian, and now Goomlandian, currently housing awesome_ketchup's small fishing village.

South East Taiga.Description: A colony in the South owned by HUM, containing the Tautona bunker.

South Farnough.Description: The Beachdom of Farnough, led by ArcherAce, is a desert kingdom in the far South.

South Polgolas.Description: South Polgolas (also known as Satama and Schavick) is the southernmost city in the CSA. Having suffered destruction during the Balkan Troubles, it is currently being rebuilt.

Spruceville.Description: A historic village in the lush spruce forests of northern Montrose.

Stemtown.Description: A ghost town in the Goomlandian province of New Toeland. Constructed as a joint project with HUM, the endeavor was abandoned when HUM did not develop their half of the town. HUM's half became Toe Gang and was later re-purchased by Goomlandia.

Sunflame's House.Description: The island estate of Montrosian citizen Sunflame_is_DED.

Tautona.Description: An underground bunker & former satellite state of Sylvia, now part of the East Taiga lands owned by HUM.

the grey sanctum.Description: the grey sanctum (formerly known as Cob Castle) is the Voidnestian castle of c0baltblue.

Toe Gang.Description: The iconic lands owned by hongstoes and ongstoes.

Tsarevets.Description: The headquarters of the IBWH, Tsarevets is a significant historic landmark and recently restored village.

Twiceland.Description: Twiceland is the pinnacle of Gothic architecture in LGS, featuring beautiful cathedrals and towering stone structures.

Vailan.Description: Vailan is an isolationist nation in the North, containing many beautifully constructed cities and villages, and serving as the main force behing the Northern Alliance. It is the primary nation holding to the beliefs of Oarfanism.

Vigi.Description: A Wohlstandian village in the Far South.

Vilnius.Description: Vilnius is the Groogelandian town settled by crazyjuplup.

Vladivostok.Description: Vladivostok is the capital of new Yugoslavia, featuring an impressive and still growing skyline, with buildings such as The World and the Vostok Financial Center.

Western End Portal.Description: The stronghold claimed by the Sylvian Union.

Winterfell.Description: Winterfell is a Vailic city built by MiksaSerbia, featuring dark towers and a PVP arena.
